21d71779cb7e159c23ab4cce9730a45500","tid":709949,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3997e3ab406fe02ba1c1aaf1ec34accc9dd768fd","tid":709949,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:57:17.000Z","msg":"世衛精神健康及物質濫用部門總監 Shekhar Saxena 強調，相關診斷並非指每日打機數小時，就會被診斷為「打機成癮」。實際上只會有少數患者，在達至以下三個主要條件，才能被診斷為有問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 醫護人員需考慮到現象出現時間、頻率、強度、長期、能否停止及當時情境等，才能被視作為打機完全失控；<br />\n2. 患者要將打機視作生活最重要一部份，而且認為比其他生活興趣和活動重要（例如作息出現問題、社交活動大幅減少等）；<br />\n3. 即使出現負面問題，仍然堅持不斷打機，甚至增加打機時數等。<br />\n<br />\n即使在短期內出現這些問題，除非情況極嚴重，否則此類徵狀需持續至少 12 個月，才可被視為打機成癮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好似全部中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1fa2840a652499533b329e453243d30f0ed9393d","tid":709949,"uid":8921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"做咩fyp 咁chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b86182eb8199f34baf3a5f1d0bfdb8d2513ce09","tid":709949,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fa2840a652499533b329e453243d30f0ed9393d","tid":709949,"uid":8921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"做咩fyp 咁chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUST<br />\n連續幾年朝早6點幾到第二朝3點幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d464dbe8ffdf77ca1dbdc19254a525f8ea76df","tid":709949,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:02:58.000Z","msg"